  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">ElNet CO exchange controller HV/generator</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The Elant CO system is designed for an efficient exchange between two power supply sources (electricity company / generator) in the event of a malfunction in one of the power supply systems.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The system is more reliable than any other replacement system.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The system saves installation of command and delay relays and lack of voltage relays, switches, voltmeters and more.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\n<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Elant CO includes a friendly color graphic screen in the Hebrew language that enables, among other things, the following actions:<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- Registration of up to 1000 alerts and electrical events including date, hour and second.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- RS485 communication for building control in an open protocol.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- Perfect protection for the generator (Double Interlock).<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- Sophisticated test software for the board manufacturer and the user to test all wiring and operations.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- The possibility of running a generator in Shabbat operation with reference to the Hebrew astronomical calendar.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- Changing parameters and timers and more.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>- For a full Israeli standard system that includes EMC and - Safety.</span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Related products</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications Ltd</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">making contact</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Phone: +972-3-6474998</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Fax: +972-3-6474598</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Email:<a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" data-auto-recognition=\"true\" href=\"mailto:cal@ddc.co.il\">cal@ddc.co.il</a></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">opening hours</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications Ltd</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Sunday - Thursday</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">08:00 - 17:00</span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:right;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">address</span></span></span></sp