  "rich_text": [
    "ElNet CO exchange controller HV/generator",
    "The Elant CO system is designed for an efficient exchange between two power supply sources (electricity company / generator) in the event of a malfunction in one of the power supply systems.\n​\nThe system is more reliable than any other replacement system.\n​\nThe system saves installation of command and delay relays and lack of voltage relays, switches, voltmeters and more.\nElant CO includes a friendly color graphic screen in the Hebrew language that enables, among other things, the following actions:\n- Registration of up to 1000 alerts and electrical events including date, hour and second.\n- RS485 communication for building control in an open protocol.\n- Perfect protection for the generator (Double Interlock).\n- Sophisticated test software for the board manufacturer and the user to test all wiring and operations.\n- The possibility of running a generator in Shabbat operation with reference to the Hebrew astronomical calendar.\n- Changing parameters and timers and more.\n- For a full Israeli standard system that includes EMC and - Safety.",
    "Related Products",
    "Control Applications Ltd",
    "making contact\nPhone: +972-3-6474998\n​\nFax: +972-3-6474598\nEmail:\ncal@ddc.co.il",
    "opening hours\nControl Applications Ltd\nSunday - Thursday\n08:00 - 17:00",
    "Address\n25 Barzel Street, Tel Aviv\n6971035\nIsrael",
    "© Copyright - Control Applications Ltd"
  ],
